# Solution on LeetCode: https://leetcode.com/problems/minimum-average-of-smallest-and-largest-elements/solutions/7028631/minimizing-pair-averages-efficient-sorti-jkj5/

class Solution:
    def minimumAverage(self, nums: List[int]) -> float:
        nums.sort()
        return min((nums[i] + nums[-i - 1]) / 2 for i in range(len(nums) // 2))
